                        <li>Grammar (Parts of Speech, Tenses, Subject-Verb Agreement, Articles, Sentence Structure)</li>
                        <li>Vocabulary (Synonyms and Antonyms, Analogies, Word Meanings)</li>
                        <li>Reading Comprehension (Understanding the Main Idea, Inference and Conclusion, Vocabulary in Context)</li>
                        <li>Sentence Correction (Error Spotting, Sentence Improvement)</li>
                        <li>Critical Reasoning (Identifying Assumptions, Strengthening and Weakening Arguments, Drawing Inferences)</li>
                        <li>Para-jumbles (Rearrangement of Sentences)</li>
                        <li>Sentence Completion (Cloze Test, Fill in the Blanks)</li>
                      </ul>                      
